Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要释放咯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.58,0:24:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Psychic{\fsp125}　{\r}\N念动力  什么什么的！
